        <strong>JPG/JPEG</strong>: Most common photo format<br>
        <strong>PNG</strong>: Supports transparency, lossless quality<br>
        <strong>WebP</strong>: Modern format, smaller file sizes<br>
        <strong>BMP, GIF, TIFF</strong>: Less common but supported</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
