        <p>Yes! You can easily reorder images:<br>
        1. Drag and drop images in the preview area<br>
        2. Use the up/down arrows on each image<br>
        3. Remove unwanted images with the √ó button<br>
        4. The order in preview = order in PDF</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
