        ‚Ä¢ Images up to 20MP process quickly<br>
        ‚Ä¢ Very high-res images may be optimized<br>
        ‚Ä¢ We recommend 150-300 DPI for print quality<br>
        ‚Ä¢ Web images (72 DPI) work fine for screen viewing<br>
        ‚Ä¢ Large images are automatically optimized for PDF</p>
      </div>
